{"title":"龙金狗和冯八两","authors":["丁力"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙金狗和冯八两"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁  力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前线战事打得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人退到黄家庙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊事员，龙金狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送罢午饭往回走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一走走到杨树村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树后跳出一个蒋匪兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙金狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声吼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“把枪放下！举起手！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪兵名叫冯八两，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连忙举手把话讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是中央兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特为来投降。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙金狗捡起了枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带他走到大路旁："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“以后不要喊‘中央兵’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改口叫做‘蒋匪军’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为匪军抢劫老百姓……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯八两小声讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“蒋匪军太不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当官的克扣粮和饷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让我们能吃饱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我本来是个庄稼人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只恨蒋介石逼着搞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁个愿意替他去打仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个想投共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我躲在山沟里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到你们来缴枪……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙金狗把他扶上坡："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你过去虽说有些错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但那不是你的过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要今天能改错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们待你很宽和。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯八两心里很欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他磨拳擦掌跟龙金狗讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要和解放军在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同出力去打贼老蒋”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九、九、一、南京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}